name: Honduran Factory 2nds Perfecto Corojo
additionalNotes: Honduran Factory 2nds cigars are your ticket to enjoying high-quality premium cigars at deep discount. The entire selection is a mix of factory leftovers from Gran Habano Cigars, manufacturers of some of the most consistently well-made and flavorful cigars west of Havana. They vary by blend, but whichever cigar shape you choose, you're assured a smooth, rich-tasting smoke handcrafted with the finest longfiller tobaccos and top-grade wrapper leaves. Perfect for every day!
